#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's &kteatime;?"
msgstr "Hvad er &kteatime;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kteatime; is a handy timer for steeping tea. No longer will you have to "
"guess at how long it takes for your tea to be ready. Simply select the type "
"of tea you have, and it will alert you when the tea is ready to drink."
msgstr ""
"&kteatime; er en praktisk tidsmåler når du laver te. Du skal ikke længere "
"gætte hvor lang tid det tager for din te at blive parat. Vælg simpelthen den "
"type te du har, og den vil gøre dig opmærksom på hvornår teen er parat til "
"at drikke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Use &kteatime;"
msgstr "Hvordan bruger man &kteatime;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start up &kteatime;, it will automatically dock itself in your "
"panel. To access the menu, right click on the docked icon. This will present "
"a list of options which are covered in more detail in the next chapter."
msgstr ""
"Når du starter &kteatime;, vil den automatisk dokke sig selv ned i dit "
"panel. For at få adgang til menuen, højreklikkes på den dokkede ikon. Dette "
"vil præsentere dig for en liste af muligheder som bliver dækket i større "
"detalje i det næste kapitel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timing Your Tea"
msgstr "Tag tid på din te"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Upon starting, the panel icon will be that of an empty tea mug. If you "
#| "click on the mug and select your tea, the icon will change to a filled "
#| "mug. After the specified time, the tea will be finished, and a suitable "
#| "message box will be shown. At this point, you can close the message box "
#| "by clicking on it and reset the timer by clicking on the icon. The mug "
#| "will be shown as empty again."
msgid ""
"Upon starting, the panel icon will be that of an tea mug. If you click with "
"the &RMB; on the mug and select your tea, an animated clock visualizing the "
"remaining time is displayed on the icon. After the specified time, the tea "
"will be finished, and a suitable message box will be shown. At this point, "
"you can close the message box by clicking on it. This resets also the timer "
"and the clock on the mug disappears again."
msgstr ""
"Efter start, viser panelikonet en tom tekande. Hvis du klikker på kanden og "
"vælger te, ændres ikonen til en fuld kande. Efter den angivne tid, er teen "
"færdig, og et passende meddelelsesfelt vises. Nu kan du lukke "
"meddelelsefeltet ved at klikke på det og nulstille tidtageren ved at klikke "
"på ikonen. Kanden vises så som tom igen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "The timer should only be reset by those who really enjoy tea."
msgstr "Tidsmåleren bør kun nulstilles af dem der virkelig kan lide te."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Options"
msgstr "Menu-tilvalg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following section describes the menu options that are available in "
"&kteatime;."
msgstr ""
"Følgende afsnit beskriver menu-tilvalgene der er til stede i &kteatime;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Your Tea"
msgstr "Vælg din te"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking on the icon with the &RMB; will bring up a menu. At the top of "
#| "the menu there are three menu items. Here, you can select what kind of "
#| "tea you are preparing to drink. There are: <guimenuitem>Black Tea</"
#| "guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, and "
#| "<guimenuitem>Fruit Tea</guimenuitem>. These teas are preconfigured with a "
#| "default time. Many people have complained that the times are not correct. "
#| "Please be aware that the amount of time it takes to steep a cup of tea is "
#| "based on personal preference. The times chosen are approximations. If you "
#| "read on, you will learn how to change or delete these predefined times "
#| "and to set your own time. A quick-and-easy way to set a custom time is to "
#| "choose <guimenuitem>Anonymous...</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgid ""
"Clicking on the icon with the &RMB; will bring up a menu. At the top of the "
"menu there are four menu items. Here, you can select what kind of tea you "
"are preparing to drink. There are: <guimenuitem>Black Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Fruit Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"and <guimenuitem>Green Tea</guimenuitem>. These teas are preconfigured with "
"a default time. Many people have complained that the times are not correct. "
"Please be aware that the amount of time it takes to steep a cup of tea is "
"based on personal preference. The times chosen are approximations. If you "
"read on, you will learn how to change or delete these predefined times and "
"to set your own time. A quick-and-easy way to set a custom time is to choose "
"<guimenuitem>Custom...</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"En menu vises ved at klikke på ikonen med højre museknap. Øverst i menuen er "
"der tre menupunkter. Her kan du vælge hvilken slags te du skal drikke. "
"Valgmulighederne er <guimenuitem>Sort te</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Earl "
"Grey</guimenuitem>, og <guimenuitem>Urtete</guimenuitem>. Tesorterne er "
"indstillede med en standardtid. Mange har klaget over at tiderne ikke er "
"rigtige. Vær rar og husk at tiden det tager at brygge en kop te er baseret "
"på personlig smag. Tiderne som er valgte er omtrentlige. Hvis du læser "
"videre, vil du lære hvordan du ændrer eller fjerner de forindstillede tider "
"og hvordan du indstiller din egen tid. En hurtig og nem måde at angive en "
"egen tid er at vælge <guimenuitem>Anonym...</guimenuitem> i menuen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guimenuitem>Configure Notifications...</guimenuitem> brings up the "
"&kde; Notification Settings for &kteatime;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the Tea Timer"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start the tea timer select a tea from the context menu. As confirmation "
"that you have indeed started the timer, a clock visualizing the remaining "
"time is displayed in the panel icon."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Indstil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens up the configuration dialog box. A screenshot is shown "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Dette menupunkt åbner indstillingsdialogen. Et skærmaftryk vises nedenfor:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kteatime;'s indstillingsdialog.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kteatime;'s indstillingsdialog.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As shown in the picture, you may add new entries for other tea or change "
"names, times and the order of existing entries. This is useful if you are "
"brewing a cup of tea that is not on the list or if you do not agree with the "
"predefined times. To edit one entry, mark it in the <guilabel>Tea List</"
"guilabel> on the left and change the values in the <guilabel>Tea Properties</"
"guilabel> on the right."
msgstr ""
"Som det ses på billedet, kan du tilføje nye indgange for en anden te, eller "
"ændre navn, tider og de eksisterende indganges rækkefølge. Dette er nyttigt "
"hvis du brygger en kop te som ikke findes i listen, eller hvis du ikke "
"synes  standardtiderne er gode. For at ændre en indgang, markeres den i "
"telisten til venstre og værdierne ændres under egenskaber for teen til højre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The box below is the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> field. Here you can "
#| "define an action that will be executed when the time is up. The button "
#| "<guibutton>Configure Events...</guibutton> brings up the &kde; "
#| "Notification Settings for &kteatime;. The <guilabel>Event</guilabel> "
#| "check box below enables the event selected in the &kde; Notification "
#| "Settings. If <guilabel>Popup</guilabel> is selected, a message box will "
#| "appear alerting you to the fact that your tea is ready. The third check "
#| "box can hold any valid system command. Probably, you will want to leave "
#| "it blank."
msgid ""
"The box below is the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> field. Here you can define "
"an action that will be executed when the time is up. If <guilabel>Popup</"
"guilabel> is selected, a message box will appear alerting you to the fact "
"that your tea is ready."
msgstr ""
"Nedenfor er feltet <guilabel>Begivenhed</guilabel>. Her kan du definere en "
"begivenhed som sker når tiden har udløbet. Knappen <guibutton>Indstil "
"begivenheder...</guibutton> viser &kde;'s meddelelseindstillinger for "
"&kteatime;. Afkrydsningsfeltet <guilabel>Begivenhed</guilabel> nedenfor "
"aktiverer begivenheden som blev valgt i &kde;'s meddelelseindstillinger. "
"Hvis <guilabel>Dialog</guilabel> markeres, vises et meddelelsesfelt som "
"fortæller dig at teen er færdig. Det tredje afkrydsningsfelt kan indeholde "
"en hvilken som helst gyldig systemkommando. Sædvanligvis efterlader du den "
"tom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you enable the check box labeled <guilabel>Visualize progress in icon "
#| "tray</guilabel>, the progress will be shown as a little animated pie "
#| "chart inside the icon."
msgid ""
"If you enable the check box labeled <guilabel>Visualize progress in icon "
"tray</guilabel>, the progress will be shown as a little animated clock "
"inside the icon."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du aktiverer feltet som hedder <guilabel>Vis fremgang i statusfeltets "
"ikon</guilabel>, vises fremgangen som et lille animeret tærtediagram inde i "
"ikonen."

